0.1.4 - 2011-10-26

 * reduce default max_lines to 2000

 * add support for multiple message arguments to info, err and warn methods.

0.1.3 - 2011-09-16

 * Extend tests for a common error case, a nil value for a section header, as could be produced by a missing environment variable

 * Allow config object to have additional keys (methods) added if they do not already exist

0.1.2 - 2011-08-25

 * Reworked Rakefile to use new rspec

 * Changed logging output format to be more consistent

 * Added spec tests for file-based logs

0.1.1 - 2011-08-05

 * Moved Logger under Datyl namespace

0.1.0 - 2011-08-18 

 * Moved Config and Reporter classes under Datyl namespace.

